      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY BREAD ROLL (3) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 2 lengths into second (22.96) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 400m. Yet to taste defeat from four runs out of this box. Rates highly and will give a great sight. BILLY BLINDERS (2) comes here off a handy win over 400m at this track in 22.84. Has the ability and looks a key chance. FULL TILT TOM (1) led throughout to score two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 16 length 6th at this track (23.91). The form out of last race has been strong. Has ability and is one of the better chances. LOCHINVAR GRACE (5) was in the money last time at Taree Super Track (17.41) in a NG, finishing a 4.5 lengths third. Already a winner from this draw.",
